hero.megamix_description:
The biggest hits Born in Moldova from the last 25 years. 
Mega Mix — an hour where legendary songs will be brought back into the spotlight through live performances by artists on stage or through innovative digital showcases.

home.title: Născut în Moldova Festival
home.description: Născut în Moldova is Our Music Festival. Its purpose is to inspire people to love Moldova. Regardless of ethnicity, language, religion, gender or age, our people are united by a sense of home and common formation.
